title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when export data from table containing highlight/map.
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from the table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception occurs in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: The data should be successfully exported from the table without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 2. Preview the attached report. 3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
